   WASHINGTON
</P>
<P>
   EAGLE _ WASHINGTON _ President Clinton announces Friday that the
bald eagle, a symbol of America, is being taken off the endangered
species list. (Deans, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   FIREWORKS _ WASHINGTON _ The fireworks business is exploding, as
