<HEADLINE>
`TROPHY' TREES: MADE-IN-THE-SHADE GRANDEUR FOR YUPPIE YARDS  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Personal-Finance and Lifestyle Editors)   (This 500-word ``separate buy'' story is from the June issue of
``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased
