   HANDYMAN-HOTTON (Undated) _ Sagging flagstone could be caused by
many factors, but an ant infestation is surely not one of them. By
Peter Hotton.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   WARSH-COLUMN (Undated) _ On the last Fourth of July celebration
of the century, what, if anything, can be said about the path that
has brought the United States to its present point? That it was
Franklin Roosevelt's century, and that Ronald Reagan was the
faithful steward of his ``mixed economy.'' By David Warsh. 1300
words.
</P>
<P>
   FINANCE-HOOKER (Undated) _ Investor's attempt at diversification
falls short. By Kenneth Hooker.
</P>
