   &UR; AUTOS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ABOUT-MOTOR-HOMES (Brighton, Mich.) _ Last year, sales of RVs,
which include everything from pop-up campers to luxurious travel
trailers, hit their highest level since 1978. Within the segment,
sales of motor homes had their best year in a decade. For the first
time in history, people in their 30s and 40s outnumber senior
citizens buying RVs, according to the Recreational Vehicle Industry
Association. By Michelle Krebs. (Moved).
</P>
