<P>
   (NYT2) WORCESTER, Mass. -- July 2, 1999 --
HOMESICK-KOSOVARS-BOS, 7-02 -- Noriqik Bacaliu, 2, stands outside
the Concordia Lutheran Church near, from left, his father Zahir,
grandmother Bahtie and great aunt Xhemile. Since NATO troops moved
